{
  "stem": "26983.13",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew one of our former boys who went a couple of years before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was one of the strongest one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was also [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was really good condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he collapsed when he went by himself to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because that was mainly our--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He collapsed there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And was weak, very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And many of us-- I mean, I know about two of our former children who had amnesia after the war and forgot everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Luckily, they wrote before, a kind of diary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They forgot everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, that's a kind of--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the one wrote a diary after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so his whole memory is in this diary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other one had, also, a blackout.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on it came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The fate of this 50, I mean, of this group, was very different.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many got something of a normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many were very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of them died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One or two committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of them had strokes, very bad strokes, are till today in very bad condition, paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some of them had, meanwhile, open-heart surgeries, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, heart surgery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One or two have, also, cancer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them died a so-called normal life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, I wanted to tell you about the meeting in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very, very-- for me--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was staying there before the crematorium, which I saw in '45, and they just with dynamite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I could recognize still the rest of [NON-ENGLISH] room and the other places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, it was clear to me how we were robbed, how they stole from us our childhoods, the whole-- and the life afterwards.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What we missed, I mean, what they took away from us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
